Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.83,0:00:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}The dreams embraced by a single life{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.84,0:00:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}are boundless beyond even the stars.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.84,0:00:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}The dreams that we foster over time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.85,0:00:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}are waiting for the moment{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}when we come upon them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.53,0:00:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}The words we exchange{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}make our hearts tremble,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.53,0:00:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}and a chance meeting{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}could change the future.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.21,0:01:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}People, no matter who they are,{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}as they pursue their dreams,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.48,0:01:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}have the courage to travel new paths.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.15,0:01:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}As we leave behind a living{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}testament of our journey,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.49,0:01:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}the Galaxy Railways on which{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}we travel continue ever on.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.85,0:01:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Louis-san!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.52,0:01:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Louis-san!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.86,0:01:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Louis!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.53,0:01:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Do we still have any reserve power?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.53,0:02:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Half of our cars are down.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Main engine output is also dropping.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.21,0:02:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Keep us up and running! Do whatever\N{\c&He1e1e1&}it takes to prevent us from crashing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.48,0:02:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuuki, scan the planet's topography.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.15,0:02:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Find us a place where we\N{\c&He1e1e1&}can make a forced landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.49,0:02:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain! Systems are down!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What!? Hey, do something, fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We're almost to the troposphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.90,0:02:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Use all of our reserve power\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to keep our frame level.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.50,0:02:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuki,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.18,0:02:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Adjusting reentry angle\N{\c&He1e1e1&}plus six degrees...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Everyone, brace for impact!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.18,0:03:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}"Ephemeral Winds"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.89,0:03:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Forced landing successful...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Let's get {\i1}Louis-san{\i0} to\N{\c&He1e1e1&}the medical car at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Louis!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.24,0:03:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.91,0:03:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Leave her alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.24,0:03:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.25,0:03:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You hurry and analyze that chip.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.22,0:04:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Figure out where that dimension hole\N{\c&He1e1e1&}is going to appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.85,0:04:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You guys hurry and get the communications\N{\c&He1e1e1&}and radar systems repaired.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.19,0:04:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Contact Headquarters once they\N{\c&He1e1e1&}are restored, and request a rescue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.20,0:04:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Do you intend to stand by\N{\c&He1e1e1&}and watch a wounded person die!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.20,0:04:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Consider the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.54,0:04:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We can't help but make\N{\c&He1e1e1&}some small sacrifices
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}in order to fulfill our mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.88,0:04:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Small sacrifices, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.55,0:04:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}With that injury\N{\c&He1e1e1&}and all the blood she has lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.21,0:04:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}there's no way she will survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.22,0:04:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Dying at her post will get her\N{\c&He1e1e1&}a two-grade promotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.55,0:04:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What are you doing!?\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Obey your orders at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.89,0:04:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You bastard! I can't take it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.23,0:04:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Have you lost your mind!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.23,0:04:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.90,0:04:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}My orders are absolute! Even if I\N{\c&He1e1e1&}have to kill anyone who goes against...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.91,0:05:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bruce, Yuuki, hurry and\N{\c&He1e1e1&}carry Louis out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.18,0:05:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuki, do everything you can for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.18,0:05:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}- Roger.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}- Roger.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}- Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.18,0:05:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bulge, why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.18,0:05:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I will take responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.52,0:05:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Director, please move your foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.86,0:05:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I will not allow her bravery\N{\c&He1e1e1&}and death to be for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.87,0:05:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}And I will do everything I can...\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to protect the lives of my crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.21,0:05:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Once we have fallen into\N{\c&He1e1e1&}the worst case scenario...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.55,0:05:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}...it is only the commander\N{\c&He1e1e1&}that should have to give his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.22,0:05:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Anyone who is not\N{\c&He1e1e1&}prepared to do that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.89,0:05:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.23,0:05:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Once upon a time, your superior officer\N{\c&He1e1e1&}launched a suicide attack
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.23,0:05:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}against an unidentified enemy, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.57,0:05:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Those that stand above the others\N{\c&He1e1e1&}should be the ones who survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:06:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuuki Wataru, wasn't it? Mercy sakes,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}that was one foolish man...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.19,0:06:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Vega Platoon, Rigel Platoon,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}and Acrux Platoon
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.09,0:06:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}have launched with Class 1 equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}They have cleared the atmosphere.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Two minutes to warp-in for Planet Coulomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What about {\i1}Big One's{\i0} transponder signal?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.20,0:06:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Still nowhere to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.54,0:06:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Open up all connections\N{\c&He1e1e1&}and continue to hail them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Have Spica Platoon standing by,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}ready to launch at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.55,0:06:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Something is approaching...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.22,0:06:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}No. It has always been{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}right there next to us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:06:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}And yet, I can't see it.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}I don't know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}She's going to need surgery\N{\c&He1e1e1&}within the next two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.83,0:07:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}There isn't enough blood for transfusion.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}The special suture apparatus,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.51,0:07:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}and the hemostat ampules were\N{\c&He1e1e1&}also lost in the battle earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.84,0:07:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Let's take her to a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.84,0:07:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It won't be possible to take her\N{\c&He1e1e1&}by land through this undeveloped area.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.51,0:07:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Louis-san's{\i0} body won't\N{\c&He1e1e1&}be able to withstand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.18,0:07:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Well, in any case, we can donate\N{\c&He1e1e1&}some blood. I'm type A-3.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.49,0:07:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What about Louis?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.52,0:07:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}There isn't anyone in Sirius Platoon\N{\c&He1e1e1&}who is a match for {\i1}Louis-san.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.87,0:07:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Um, {\i1}Bruce-san!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.54,0:07:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.87,0:07:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.87,0:07:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuki, we've got two hours, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}B- {\i1}Bruce-san!{\i0} Please wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.54,0:07:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Everything's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.55,0:07:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Louis, don't you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.17,0:08:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You'd better get yourself ready for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You can't mean... Louis will\N{\c&He1e1e1&}definitely pull through!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.84,0:08:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Not that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}This doesn't just go as far as Louis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.51,0:08:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}If what she said is true,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.51,0:08:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}then this is going to be the biggest task\N{\c&He1e1e1&}the SDF has had since it started.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.18,0:08:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Defending the Galaxy Railways against\N{\c&He1e1e1&}invaders from another dimension...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.19,0:08:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It means that we will be fighting\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to protect the entire universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.19,0:08:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The whole... universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.20,0:08:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That's right. Including these guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.20,0:08:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Stop! Let me go! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.54,0:08:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.54,0:08:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Let me go! Stop! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.21,0:08:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.21,0:08:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Don't leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.21,0:08:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Of all times!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.55,0:09:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.17,0:09:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You're SDF!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.18,0:09:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You guys are out of your jurisdiction!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.85,0:09:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}If you've got more youth than\N{\c&He1e1e1&}you can handle, come join the SDF.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.82,0:09:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We'll welcome you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.19,0:09:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Thank you for saving me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.19,0:09:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Hitchhiking is fine and all, but be\N{\c&He1e1e1&}more choosy about which car you get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.19,0:09:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.53,0:09:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Good grief, it's because\N{\c&He1e1e1&}of idiots like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.87,0:09:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What do you mean, idiot!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.53,0:09:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That's no attitude to cop\N{\c&He1e1e1&}after we saved you, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.21,0:09:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Let it go. We're in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.54,0:10:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bruce...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.22,0:10:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Hey, you, aren't you\N{\c&He1e1e1&}going a little too fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.22,0:10:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}There's somebody's life at stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.90,0:10:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That is the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.57,0:10:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Louis, I'm sorry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.25,0:10:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuuki... {\i1}- kun...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.60,0:10:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain, as far as analyzing\N{\c&He1e1e1&}the Cosmo Matrix goes,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.60,0:10:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}we won't be able to manage it unless\N{\c&He1e1e1&}we get it back to Headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.74,0:11:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}and leave it to the appropriate division.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.27,0:11:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Big One's{\i0} equipment just isn't up to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.54,0:11:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.21,0:11:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.55,0:11:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The Sutherland star system, huh?\N{\c&He1e1e1&}We sure did come a long way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.22,0:11:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}...please come in! This is\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Galaxy Railways Headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Sirius Platoon, can you hear me?\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Please come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.56,0:11:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}This is SDF Sirius Platoon, {\i1}Big One.{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&}You're five by five.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.23,0:11:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You're all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.23,0:11:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yeah. We made a forced landing\N{\c&He1e1e1&}on Sutherland's fourth planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.90,0:11:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We'll send assistance right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.91,0:11:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Please do. One more thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.31,0:11:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}suspend all service to\N{\c&He1e1e1&}the lines near Coulomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.78,0:11:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}There's still one battleship there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Their weapons are...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.91,0:11:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Vega, Rigel, and Acrux Platoons\N{\c&He1e1e1&}are currently headed there
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.05,0:11:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}with Class 1 equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.26,0:11:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Don't let them go there! Call them back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.21,0:12:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}All hands, battle stations!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.54,0:12:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}If they try anything,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}we're taking them on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.21,0:12:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.57,0:12:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Commence attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.54,0:13:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I've lost contact with Acrux Platoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.21,0:13:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Murase, pull out of there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.21,0:13:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Is that you, Bulge!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.21,0:13:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We can't beat them\N{\c&He1e1e1&}with the weapons we have now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.22,0:13:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}My old platoon has been wiped out!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}I can't just tuck tail and leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.89,0:13:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You've got to bear with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}If you withdraw, we'll have\N{\c&He1e1e1&}a chance of beating them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.72,0:13:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Right now, just shut up\N{\c&He1e1e1&}and get out of there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.56,0:13:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Murase! Don't you die, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.90,0:13:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The enemy ship is disappearing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.57,0:13:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.91,0:13:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.19,0:14:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}This is the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.53,0:14:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.87,0:14:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Hold on, you're!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.54,0:14:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Hey! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.54,0:14:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Hey, stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.55,0:14:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You're injured, aren't you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.21,0:14:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bruce, don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.55,0:14:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Getting hit by a ricochet\N{\c&He1e1e1&}is so embarrassing,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.36,0:14:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}how could I say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}And so, to let Yuki concentrate\N{\c&He1e1e1&}on treating Louis...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.89,0:14:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}My wound was not as severe as hers.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.56,0:14:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}With something this minor, I can\N{\c&He1e1e1&}keep going until tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.90,0:14:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What are you talking about!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.90,0:14:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Don't start blubbering.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.14,0:14:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You won't be able to keep it together\N{\c&He1e1e1&}for what's ahead like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.91,0:14:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Don't be an ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.24,0:15:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.55,0:15:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'd really like to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.88,0:15:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Not at all! You have wonderful skill.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}I didn't even need to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.89,0:15:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You can't mean that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.89,0:15:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Go stay next to Louis.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.23,0:15:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.56,0:15:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I hear she got through\N{\c&He1e1e1&}the procedure safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.23,0:15:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Then Louis is going to live, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.23,0:15:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.24,0:16:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}For crying out loud, I've never\N{\c&He1e1e1&}seen such an idiotic man before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.84,0:16:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Idiotic? What do you mean, idiotic?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.84,0:16:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You've been hurt a lot, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.85,0:16:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.18,0:16:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}A little.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.52,0:16:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Ever since I was a kid,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}I've been acting like a mercenary...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}to keep myself alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.85,0:16:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}All I've ever held\N{\c&He1e1e1&}in this hand is my gun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.53,0:16:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}...and this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.20,0:16:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}By any chance, is that\N{\c&He1e1e1&}a memento of someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.20,0:16:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That must be your precious\N{\c&He1e1e1&}good-luck charm, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.54,0:16:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.21,0:16:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Now listen, you've got\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to get three days' rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.91,0:16:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'll contact the SDF people for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.88,0:16:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.55,0:16:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It looks good on you, in its own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.22,0:16:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I just got assigned here today.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}You're my first patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.23,0:17:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Coupling with {\i1}Big One{\i0} complete.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Prepare to launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}But I heard from that cute {\i1}nurse-chan{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.94,0:17:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}that you would be in\N{\c&He1e1e1&}the hospital for a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}No way I'm doing that.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}This is just a scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.51,0:17:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm coming back now. Wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.85,0:17:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Painkillers and antibiotics.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Make sure you take them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.85,0:17:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Thanks for looking after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.19,0:17:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Now we're even.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.53,0:17:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Next time, let me hear you\N{\c&He1e1e1&}play your harmonica.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.87,0:17:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It will cost you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.20,0:17:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I can pay you with my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That won't even get you a single measure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What does that mean!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You guessed right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.55,0:17:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}No matter how hard I prayed,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.51,0:17:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}this thing was never able to\N{\c&He1e1e1&}protect a single one of my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}For the first time,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}one of my prayers got through.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:18:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.16,0:18:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bye now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.16,0:18:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'll see you again, right, Bruce?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}If you're a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.50,0:18:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Geez, he's treating me like a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.87,0:20:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.54,0:20:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.88,0:20:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}David...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Louis...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.55,0:20:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.56,0:20:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I don't want... to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.90,0:20:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Thank you, {\i1}Yuuki-kun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.57,0:20:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What are you talking about?\N{\c&He1e1e1&}We're friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.90,0:20:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}No... we're more than friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.91,0:20:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I think of you all as family now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.25,0:20:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm really glad I was\N{\c&He1e1e1&}assigned to Sirius Platoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.59,0:20:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}So am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.26,0:20:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}But don't tell Bruce.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.93,0:20:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.27,0:21:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}He'll probably yell at me again\N{\c&He1e1e1&}for being too needy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.21,0:21:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}The man they called the Grim Reaper...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.88,0:21:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Now, his destiny has reached its end.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.89,0:21:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}No one to see him off...{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}no farewell flowers...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.23,0:21:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}The only thing there for him was{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}the blowing of ephemeral winds.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.24,0:21:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}How many nights have{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}I spent alone since then?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.25,0:22:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Constantly having dreams of the hope{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}that you are, as I lightly sleep.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.93,0:22:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}The smiles and tears{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}that you gave to me and me alone{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.94,0:22:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}come to mind every time{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}I get disheartened,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.28,0:22:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}and I set forth again toward the morrow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.95,0:22:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}The joyful light of the galaxy beckons me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.56,0:22:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}to that beloved person within my heart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.57,0:22:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}No matter how far apart we are,{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}my memories will never fade.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.24,0:23:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}My heart wishes always{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}to be at your side.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.86,0:23:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}"Next Time"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.46,0:23:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Bulge-kun, your crime in{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}disobeying orders is a serious one.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.47,0:23:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Everything is being{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}taken out of your hands.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.47,0:23:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}But, I!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.81,0:23:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Next time on Tales of the Galaxy Railways,{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Episode 23:{\i0} "Harsh Verdict"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.81,0:23:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}We're going to encounter{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}something at the next station.{\i0}